<html><head><title>The Guide Program Needs You!</title></head><body class="newsbody" ><div class=newbody><h2>EverQuest Vault -- EQ </h3><h3>The Guide Program Needs You!</h3><p>Once again SOE has put out the call for new Volunteer Guides.  Here's the <a href="http://eqlive.station.sony.com/community/dev_view.jsp?id=64355">full post</a>.<blockquote>Hail and well met citizens of Norrath!<br><br>Do you travel the land seeking new challenges?  Do you wonder what it might be like to don a mask and adventure behind the scenes? Does the thought of entertaining others by telling a story or weaving an adventure appeal to you?<br><br>The EverQuest Guide Program is looking for more energetic individuals to help us bring more fun and adventure to Norrath. We're growing and changing and we can't do it alone. We need your help to bring more magic to the world of Norrath!<br><br>Ready to join us? Step forward and fill out an application today! <a href="https://guide.everquest.com/guideapp/">Guide Application</a></blockquote><br>If you think you can make EQ better for players here's your chance, be sure to check it out!</div><p><div classs=copyright><font face=arial size=2 color=#959595>News Story from EverQuest Vault -- EQ <br>News Date: Tue 30 Nov 2004<br>Link: http://eqvault.ign.com//index.php#3837<br>Printed On: Wed Dec 8 4:37:30 PST 2004<br>©2004 IGN Entertainment</font></span>